{"tid":258664,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"2016-17 LIHKG香港乙組女神聯賽升班附決賽-周慧敏vs游蕙禎","createTime":"2017-05-26T10:00:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T04:49:37.000Z","uid":92376,"like":26,"dislike":75,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ce3acc7d3f35815eb4c7f9c31321264bf425dc1c","tid":258664,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T10:00:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">LIHKG香港乙組女神聯賽升班附加賽決賽</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-5-26 *括號內數字為聯賽最終排名</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/lXgAk8o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FlXgAk8o.png&h=e531dede&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/zyUEMKw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FzyUEMKw.png&h=79514674&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(6)周慧敏vs游蕙禎(7)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">升班附加賽決賽賽時為六小時，會員可於本帖發起後六小時內於以正負評方式(前者正評;後者負評)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的正負評投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">附加賽不設額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"62d05a427df4aea9f70debd818c736c589df9f44","tid":258664,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T10:00:44.000Z","msg":"其餘升班附加賽賽程請參閱下址<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/248638/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/248638/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"540828d747f59321fa29c3e77fa2b37fd77a935c","tid":258664,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T10:01:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norm